Package: fraccampaignsimulator
Type: Project
Title: Frac Campaign Planning Simulator
Version: 16.0.0
Description: Monte Carlo simulator for hydraulic fracturing campaign
    planning (conventional vs. zipper execution, resource queue
    simulation, historical learning, Bayesian updating, decision
    support). Not a distributable R package -- this DESCRIPTION exists
    solely as the single source of truth for dependencies, consumed by
    run_local.R and (optionally) renv.
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
